    "title": "Bug Fixes for OG Season 8 ",
    "preview_text": "Hey OGs! We’ve been keeping a close eye on reports of bugs or inconsistencies surfaced by the community and wanted to share an update on what’s been fixed or what’s coming soon. Take a look at what",
    "cover_url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HE7fOfVa0AA0y5h.jpg",
    "content_state": {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "djnec",
          "text": "Hey OGs! We’ve been keeping a close eye on reports of bugs or inconsistencies surfaced by the community and wanted to share an update on what’s been fixed or what’s coming soon. Take a look at what we’re tracking below:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 0,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "bjt55",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 1,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 27,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "7lp7n",
          "text": "✅ Already Fixed or Adjusted",
          "type": "header-one"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "bmerr",
          "text": "The OG Lobby background now shows up correctly",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "60oh4",
          "text": "Enabled the Common and Uncommon Heavy Assault Rifle rarities",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 53,
              "offset": 81,
              "style": "Italic"
            }
          ],
          "key": "5oobu",
          "text": "Muted hitmarker sounds that were incorrectly playing for everyone in the match - a full fix for this is coming in the next game update",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6bcut",
          "text": "Boom Bow’s draw time and spread has been improved",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "e4hjr",
          "text": "Scoped Assault Rifle’s recoil has been improved",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "7jclv",
          "text": "Infantry Rifle’s ADS spread and accuracy at lower rarities have been improved",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9gpre",
          "text": "Both Compact and Suppressed SMGs’ structure damage fall-off have been improved",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "dblrm",
          "text": "Hand Cannon's damage has been improved at medium-range distances",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "fg42h",
          "text": "Suppressed Pistols are now more accurate",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "aq6um",
          "text": "Rocket Launchers are now more accurate",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "am6a1",
          "text": "Assault Rifle’s recoil and recovery speed has been improved",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "bs9tv",
          "text": "Reduced Reboot Van use time from 15 to intended 10 seconds",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "5nvoe",
          "text": "Material caps have been lowered to 500 per material type",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3qpon",
          "text": "Later this week, being rebooted will no longer block you from shooting, crouching, building and other actions",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 6,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            },
            {
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 32,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "elj81",
          "text": "Note: You’ll again be respawning in the air due to this change. We’re working on a full fix to restore spawning on top of the Reboot Van",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "5fo94",
          "text": "Later this week, your character’s animations will no longer glitch if you’re launched upward by the Volcano updraft or a geyser while on a Vehicle",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 2,
              "length": 2,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 44,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "ddua8",
          "text": "⏭️ Fixed in a Future Game Update This Season",
          "type": "header-one"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "7t5hi",
          "text": "The ammo cap will be brought closer to Chapter 1 values",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "8g8om",
          "text": "Flint-Knock Pistol’s knockback will be toned down for both the wielder and the opponent",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "cfqck",
          "text": "Sniper scopes will be reverted to the Chapter 1 version for improved visibility",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2f4mc",
          "text": "The Rocket Launcher will use the correct firing audio",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "12p9f",
          "text": "Item icons featured on Vending Machines will no longer appear stretched",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2svgr",
          "text": "Removing the Vending Machine incorrectly placed at Dusty Divot",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "30sdo",
          "text": "Fixing Driftboard spawn locations at Retail Row",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4ahpt",
          "text": "Entering deep water around Loot Lake and Lazy Lagoon will have the intended slowdown effect that prevents sprinting or sliding",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "ce0pu",
          "text": "The currently-missing Reboot Van will return to Paradise Palms",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4obul",
          "text": "Reducing the number of tiles, buildings and trees incorrectly covered with snow",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2534f",
          "text": "Fixing terrain clipping in the hidden Tomato Tunnel room",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2kj0r",
          "text": "Some sidewalk tiles will no longer have colors incorrectly based on their biome",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "8b092",
          "text": "Grass will no longer clip through sidewalks and roads at Paradise Palms",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "enqbi",
          "text": "Cars in the Tomato Tunnel lava will display charred effects",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 8,
              "offset": 4,
              "style": "Italic"
            }
          ],
          "key": "dp20m",
          "text": "The Boneyard sign will be back at Junk Junction",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6ktui",
          "text": "Fixing texture mismatch around the shack east of Loot Lake",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 14,
              "offset": 17,
              "style": "Italic"
            }
          ],
          "key": "1s53v",
          "text": "Removing the old Grand Opening decorations at Dusty Diner",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 3,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 21,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "9inaf",
          "text": "🔎 Still Investigating",
          "type": "header-one"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "euie",
          "text": "Chest opening times mismatch with Chapter 1 timing",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "8ceqn",
          "text": "The Flint-Knock Pistol is currently using projectile firing mode instead of hitscan",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3fd78",
          "text": "The Northern Lights are currently less visible at night than intended",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "adhsh",
          "text": "Paradise Palms grass color mismatch",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "d77go",
          "text": "Buried Treasure can sometimes spawn under terrain and may not be dug up easily",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "56i79",
          "text": "A small mound is missing from Loot Lake… Where did it go?",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6b059",
          "text": "",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
